subject: Diving (Sports Event)
Awards, Decorations and Honors
lead_paragraph: On the final day of competition at the USA Diving Grand Prix in Fort Lauderdale, Fla., Australians took home two gold medals and a silver, with a Russian winning the only other gold medal awarded.
